1
00:01:24,900 --> 00:01:30,420
"Sammy's Children's Day"

2
00:01:30,940 --> 00:01:33,940
(Episode 3)

3
00:01:41,239 --> 00:01:42,239
Dad.

4
00:01:43,799 --> 00:01:44,799
Dad.

5
00:02:08,120 --> 00:02:09,120
Dad.

6
00:02:11,360 --> 00:02:12,360
Dad.

7
00:02:14,199 --> 00:02:14,840
Save him!

8
00:02:14,919 --> 00:02:16,159
Don't ask me anymore.

9
00:02:19,879 --> 00:02:20,879
Hurry up!

10
00:02:24,159 --> 00:02:24,759
Chusan.

11
00:02:25,039 --> 00:02:26,400
Who exactly is this person?

12
00:02:26,680 --> 00:02:27,560
This is a gunshot wound!

13
00:02:27,639 --> 00:02:28,718
Are you hurt?

14
00:02:28,719 --> 00:02:29,479
I'm fine.

15
00:02:29,480 --> 00:02:30,560
Hurry up and save him, Dad!

16
00:02:47,120 --> 00:02:49,159
The angle of this bullet is tricky.

17
00:02:49,879 --> 00:02:51,919
My far-sightedness is
making it hard to see clearly.

18
00:02:53,080 --> 00:02:55,319
How about you help him take it out?

19
00:02:55,759 --> 00:02:56,199
I...

20
00:02:56,759 --> 00:02:57,639
Saving him is more important.
Hurry up!

21
00:02:58,599 --> 00:02:59,039
Give it to me!
Hurry up, hurry up!

22
00:02:59,800 --> 00:03:00,800
Be quick!

23
00:03:03,159 --> 00:03:04,159
Come on!

24
00:03:13,120 --> 00:03:14,120
Find it first.

25
00:03:14,199 --> 00:03:15,199
Disinfect it first.

26
00:03:44,599 --> 00:03:45,599
Dad.

27
00:03:46,240 --> 00:03:46,680
It's okay.
Take a deep breath.

28
00:03:47,520 --> 00:03:48,520
Take a deep breath.

29
00:03:49,280 --> 00:03:50,440
You need to push the tweezers

30
00:03:50,599 --> 00:03:52,039
all the way to the bottom in one go.

31
00:03:52,680 --> 00:03:54,015
When you feel it touch the bullet,

32
00:03:54,039 --> 00:03:55,159
immediately squeeze it tight

33
00:03:55,319 --> 00:03:56,319
and pull it out quickly.

34
00:03:56,520 --> 00:03:57,520
Be quick and decisive.

35
00:03:58,240 --> 00:03:59,840
We can't let the wound get hurt again.

36
00:04:00,319 --> 00:04:01,319
Hurry up.

37
00:04:05,360 --> 00:04:06,360
Pull it out.

38
00:04:18,800 --> 00:04:19,800
Stop the bleeding.

39
00:04:26,480 --> 00:04:27,560
All done, all done.

40
00:04:29,163 --> 00:04:31,417
[He Family Doctor]

41
00:04:47,040 --> 00:04:48,800
How did you get involved
with such a person?

42
00:04:49,319 --> 00:04:51,319
And you brought him home?

43
00:04:55,199 --> 00:04:56,399
He saved me before.

44
00:04:57,399 --> 00:04:58,399
What happened to you?

45
00:04:58,600 --> 00:04:59,600
He saved you?

46
00:05:00,399 --> 00:05:02,560
I was robbed before.

47
00:05:03,519 --> 00:05:04,800
He chased them away.

48
00:05:09,360 --> 00:05:10,720
I already told you before.

49
00:05:10,839 --> 00:05:12,759
If they want to rob, just give it to them.

50
00:05:12,793 --> 00:05:13,793
Dad.

51
00:05:13,920 --> 00:05:15,759
Didn't you teach me to repay kindness?

52
00:05:19,720 --> 00:05:20,839
I've done everything I can.

53
00:05:21,319 --> 00:05:22,319
Next,

54
00:05:22,839 --> 00:05:23,680
we'll see if this little brat

55
00:05:23,800 --> 00:05:24,839
has a tough enough life.

56
00:05:26,920 --> 00:05:27,920
The mafia.

57
00:05:28,120 --> 00:05:29,240
They're all debt collectors.

58
00:05:31,399 --> 00:05:32,519
You should rest early too.

59
00:06:18,319 --> 00:06:20,279
Aren't you the mighty Twinblade Xia?

60
00:06:22,560 --> 00:06:23,720
How did you end up like this?

61
00:08:13,319 --> 00:08:13,839
Chusan,
he's still not awake?

62
00:08:14,879 --> 00:08:15,879
No.

63
00:09:20,024 --> 00:09:21,697
[He Chusan]

64
00:09:24,960 --> 00:09:26,600
This damn kid.

65
00:09:30,519 --> 00:09:32,080
Wild horse splitting its mane.

66
00:09:34,039 --> 00:09:36,000
Your horse stance has to be firm.

67
00:09:36,879 --> 00:09:37,879
Right.

68
00:09:38,360 --> 00:09:38,879
Good.

69
00:09:39,159 --> 00:09:40,159
Next move.

70
00:09:40,200 --> 00:09:41,200
Listen up!

71
00:09:41,759 --> 00:09:43,200
White crane spreads its wings.

72
00:09:45,679 --> 00:09:46,919
Raise your hands higher.

73
00:09:47,399 --> 00:09:48,399
Right.

74
00:09:49,000 --> 00:09:49,960
This is it.

75
00:09:49,961 --> 00:09:51,720
Your legs, don't shake.

76
00:09:52,720 --> 00:09:53,839
Good, now continue.

77
00:09:53,840 --> 00:09:55,720
Wave your hands like playing the pipa.

78
00:09:57,519 --> 00:09:58,519
Good.

79
00:09:58,960 --> 00:10:00,000
Next move.

80
00:10:07,320 --> 00:10:08,320
Come on, keep practicing.

81
00:10:09,480 --> 00:10:11,000
Focus, stop looking around.

82
00:10:12,399 --> 00:10:13,456
Master, you practice first.

83
00:10:13,480 --> 00:10:14,640
I have some things at school.

84
00:10:14,759 --> 00:10:15,759
Alright, alright.

85
00:10:27,200 --> 00:10:28,200
You're awake.

86
00:10:29,679 --> 00:10:30,679
How do you feel?

87
00:10:37,399 --> 00:10:40,120
What exactly happened?

88
00:10:41,480 --> 00:10:42,720
How did you get hurt like this?

89
00:10:49,639 --> 00:10:50,959
Where are Xiao Ma and the others?

90
00:10:51,919 --> 00:10:52,919
And your sister?

91
00:11:10,000 --> 00:11:11,000
Beef tripe.

92
00:11:14,000 --> 00:11:15,039
I want beef tripe.

93
00:11:17,120 --> 00:11:18,120
Okay.

94
00:11:42,240 --> 00:11:42,840
Is it ready, Sister Fei?

95
00:11:43,120 --> 00:11:44,535
Coming right up, I'll serve it to you.

96
00:11:44,559 --> 00:11:45,559
I'll beat you to death.

97
00:11:46,480 --> 00:11:47,480
Let's go.

98
00:11:48,799 --> 00:11:49,799
Seen this person before?

99
00:11:50,039 --> 00:11:51,039
No.

100
00:11:53,080 --> 00:11:54,480
Sister Fei, hurry up!

101
00:11:55,080 --> 00:11:56,080
Seen this person before?

102
00:11:58,039 --> 00:11:58,399
No.
Look carefully.

103
00:11:59,360 --> 00:11:59,879
Never seen him.
Really?

104
00:12:01,279 --> 00:12:02,279
No.

105
00:12:03,279 --> 00:12:04,799
Your dad had cancer back then.

106
00:12:04,960 --> 00:12:06,735
Your mom went door to
door begging for money.

107
00:12:06,759 --> 00:12:08,038
Whoever had money gave it.

108
00:12:08,039 --> 00:12:08,679
Whoever had strength helped.

109
00:12:08,799 --> 00:12:10,015
Now you're acting all high and mighty.

110
00:12:10,039 --> 00:12:11,080
Trying to show off, huh?

111
00:12:11,399 --> 00:12:12,678
Ask your dad's spirit in heaven

112
00:12:12,679 --> 00:12:13,200
if he recognizes you.

113
00:12:13,399 --> 00:12:14,639
You bitch, what did you say?

114
00:12:14,840 --> 00:12:16,279
Come on, say it! Say it!

115
00:12:16,360 --> 00:12:17,120
What did you say? Say it.

116
00:12:17,159 --> 00:12:18,159
Say it louder!

117
00:12:19,159 --> 00:12:19,960
A few bucks, she'll remember forever.
Exactly.

118
00:12:20,600 --> 00:12:21,159
No wonder you're poor.
Say it louder, come on!

119
00:12:22,240 --> 00:12:23,240
Go, go, go.

120
00:12:42,480 --> 00:12:44,840
Ah Hao, did I hurt you?

121
00:12:45,639 --> 00:12:47,320
A real man doesn't mind a small injury.

122
00:12:47,799 --> 00:12:49,480
This small injury is nothing.

123
00:12:49,679 --> 00:12:51,559
Sister, don't worry.

124
00:12:52,240 --> 00:12:54,679
Even if it's just a scrape,

125
00:12:54,960 --> 00:12:56,840
I'm always worried about you.

126
00:13:01,720 --> 00:13:02,399
Ah Hao.

127
00:13:02,600 --> 00:13:03,919
Does it still hurt now?

128
00:13:04,480 --> 00:13:06,480
Sister, it doesn't hurt anymore.

129
00:13:15,000 --> 00:13:15,840
Before you eat the beef tripe,

130
00:13:15,919 --> 00:13:16,919
take your medicine first.

131
00:13:22,799 --> 00:13:23,799
Open it.

132
00:13:34,840 --> 00:13:36,960
There are a lot of gangsters
outside looking for you.

133
00:13:51,399 --> 00:13:52,399
They said you

134
00:13:53,360 --> 00:13:54,919
are a traitor of the Xiaoqi Hall.

135
00:13:57,919 --> 00:13:58,919
Water.

136
00:14:25,000 --> 00:14:25,679
Why?

137
00:14:25,720 --> 00:14:26,720
Cigarettes.

138
00:14:32,840 --> 00:14:33,840
No cigarettes.

139
00:14:35,159 --> 00:14:36,159
You're injured.

140
00:14:36,360 --> 00:14:37,360
You can't smoke.

141
00:14:37,879 --> 00:14:38,879
Give me cigarettes.

142
00:14:42,039 --> 00:14:43,039
If you smoke,

143
00:14:43,159 --> 00:14:44,319
the medicine will be useless.

144
00:14:46,559 --> 00:14:47,559
Cigarettes.

145
00:14:53,480 --> 00:14:54,480
No cigarettes.

146
00:14:56,200 --> 00:14:57,200
It's bad for your health.

147
00:15:06,360 --> 00:15:07,399
Get your body better.

148
00:15:09,080 --> 00:15:10,080
Then hurry up and go.

149
00:15:48,000 --> 00:15:49,000
Bro.

150
00:15:55,840 --> 00:15:56,840
Bro.

151
00:15:57,320 --> 00:15:58,320
Bro.

152
00:15:58,600 --> 00:15:59,600
Sister.

153
00:16:00,480 --> 00:16:01,480
Sister.

154
00:16:04,080 --> 00:16:05,080
Bro.

155
00:16:05,159 --> 00:16:06,159
Sister.

156
00:16:06,759 --> 00:16:07,759
Sister.

157
00:16:08,120 --> 00:16:08,480
Bro.

158
00:16:08,840 --> 00:16:09,840
Sister.

159
00:16:12,480 --> 00:16:13,520
How did you bleed so much?

160
00:16:14,000 --> 00:16:15,000
Sister.

161
00:16:17,159 --> 00:16:18,159
I'll go call Dad.

162
00:16:26,200 --> 00:16:27,200
Don't go.

163
00:16:37,000 --> 00:16:38,000
I'm not leaving.

164
00:16:39,039 --> 00:16:40,039
I'll get you some water.

165
00:17:48,240 --> 00:17:49,359
You were calling for

166
00:17:49,920 --> 00:17:51,480
your brother and sister in your dream.

167
00:17:55,480 --> 00:17:56,480
Where are they?

168
00:17:57,480 --> 00:17:58,519
They're dead.

169
00:18:06,759 --> 00:18:07,759
Before, I

170
00:18:09,160 --> 00:18:10,319
lived in Xitou Lane.

171
00:18:17,720 --> 00:18:18,720
When I was little,

172
00:18:22,072 --> 00:18:24,233
I was always thinking
about how to fill my stomach.

173
00:18:30,799 --> 00:18:31,799
My dad

174
00:18:34,119 --> 00:18:35,240
was a drug addict.

175
00:18:37,119 --> 00:18:38,119
He did drugs.

176
00:18:38,880 --> 00:18:39,880
He gambled.

177
00:18:40,519 --> 00:18:41,519
He drank heavily.

178
00:18:44,240 --> 00:18:45,240
And my mom.

179
00:18:46,920 --> 00:18:48,160
After giving birth to me,

180
00:18:49,200 --> 00:18:50,400
she ran off with someone else.

181
00:18:53,039 --> 00:18:54,960
My sister is three years older than me.

182
00:18:57,160 --> 00:18:58,559
When other children

183
00:18:59,000 --> 00:19:00,519
were still clueless,

184
00:19:03,680 --> 00:19:05,118
she already knew how to cook noodles

185
00:19:05,119 --> 00:19:06,119
to comfort me.

186
00:19:09,640 --> 00:19:11,119
My dad often beat us.

187
00:19:13,119 --> 00:19:14,599
He made us steal things for him.

188
00:19:16,480 --> 00:19:17,480
If we couldn't steal,

189
00:19:18,839 --> 00:19:20,160
he would beat us severely.

190
00:19:21,880 --> 00:19:24,119
My sister always stood in front of me.

191
00:19:24,799 --> 00:19:26,879
She got beaten so badly
she couldn't get out of bed.

192
00:19:31,720 --> 00:19:33,119
When I was ten,

193
00:19:37,000 --> 00:19:38,000
my dad

194
00:19:39,160 --> 00:19:40,920
wanted to sell my
sister to be a prostitute.

195
00:19:43,792 --> 00:19:45,512
I grabbed her and ran away.

196
00:19:47,519 --> 00:19:48,839
He caught me and brought me back.

197
00:19:50,640 --> 00:19:51,920
It happened in an alley.

198
00:19:53,119 --> 00:19:54,240
He almost beat me to death.

199
00:20:00,000 --> 00:20:01,119
Dad, stop hitting me.

200
00:20:07,079 --> 00:20:08,079
I'll kill you!

201
00:20:09,079 --> 00:20:10,159
Get out of the way!

202
00:20:10,160 --> 00:20:11,160
Don't block the way.

203
00:20:13,599 --> 00:20:14,599
Trying to run again?

204
00:20:14,880 --> 00:20:15,880
You still want to run?

205
00:20:16,519 --> 00:20:17,519
Still running?

206
00:20:17,960 --> 00:20:18,960
I'll kill you!

207
00:20:21,039 --> 00:20:21,359
Brother Long!

208
00:20:21,880 --> 00:20:22,880
Brother Long!

209
00:20:23,319 --> 00:20:23,640
Brother Long!

210
00:20:24,039 --> 00:20:25,480
Ah Hao, are you okay?

211
00:20:25,839 --> 00:20:27,640
Are you all right?

212
00:20:28,200 --> 00:20:29,360
It was Qinglong who saved me.

213
00:20:31,079 --> 00:20:32,480
He just glanced at my dad.

214
00:20:33,359 --> 00:20:35,359
My dad immediately
knelt and kowtowed to him.

215
00:20:38,799 --> 00:20:40,239
Let me treat you to some cake, okay?

216
00:20:40,799 --> 00:20:41,799
Brother Long.

217
00:20:42,039 --> 00:20:43,799
Brother Long, please
spare me, Brother Long.

218
00:21:24,160 --> 00:21:25,160
Go ahead and eat.

219
00:21:31,400 --> 00:21:32,400
What are your names?

220
00:21:32,680 --> 00:21:33,759
I'm Xia Xiaoman.

221
00:21:34,119 --> 00:21:35,119
He's called Ah Hao.

222
00:21:35,160 --> 00:21:36,039
I'm not called Ah Hao.
He gave me that name.

223
00:21:36,760 --> 00:21:37,799
Be good, Ah Hao.

224
00:21:39,920 --> 00:21:41,480
If you dislike the name Ah Hao so much…

225
00:21:41,799 --> 00:21:42,879
Then what name do you want?

226
00:21:43,960 --> 00:21:44,960
Call me…

227
00:21:45,200 --> 00:21:46,200
Call me…

228
00:21:46,400 --> 00:21:47,160
Call me Cake.

229
00:21:47,200 --> 00:21:48,200
I like cake.

230
00:21:48,279 --> 00:21:49,279
Then I'll be called Cake.

231
00:21:50,559 --> 00:21:52,479
There are so many
delicious things in the world.

232
00:21:52,559 --> 00:21:54,015
So you just want to be named
after what you like to eat?

233
00:21:54,039 --> 00:21:55,400
I don't care, I don't care.

234
00:21:55,599 --> 00:21:56,880
I'll be called Cake.

235
00:21:56,920 --> 00:21:58,119
Because I like cake.

236
00:21:59,279 --> 00:22:00,279
Then how about this.

237
00:22:00,359 --> 00:22:01,639
I'll call you Liuyi from now on.

238
00:22:01,720 --> 00:22:03,360
Every day we'll celebrate Children's Day.

239
00:22:03,519 --> 00:22:05,239
And I'll treat you to cake every day, okay?

240
00:22:05,319 --> 00:22:06,359
Okay.

241
00:22:21,720 --> 00:22:22,720
He said

242
00:22:23,839 --> 00:22:24,839
June 1st

243
00:22:25,960 --> 00:22:26,960
is Children's Day.

244
00:22:34,000 --> 00:22:35,000
It belongs to me.

245
00:22:37,119 --> 00:22:38,839
It's a holiday for me and my sister.

246
00:22:49,839 --> 00:22:51,480
Later, we moved into the old house.

247
00:22:52,519 --> 00:22:53,519
Here.

248
00:22:54,000 --> 00:22:55,600
Where do you want to reach by next year?

249
00:22:55,799 --> 00:22:57,599
This year, you're at this height.

250
00:22:58,880 --> 00:22:59,880
Here.

251
00:22:59,920 --> 00:23:00,920
This tall.

252
00:23:01,880 --> 00:23:03,240
Then I'll lift you to this height.

253
00:23:04,319 --> 00:23:05,920
Xiaoman wants to grow this tall.

254
00:23:07,200 --> 00:23:08,000
Ah Hao wants to

255
00:23:08,200 --> 00:23:09,240
be taller than you.

256
00:23:14,000 --> 00:23:15,720
Big brother knew that sister loved singing.

257
00:23:17,599 --> 00:23:18,960
So he sent her to study the arts.

258
00:23:21,200 --> 00:23:23,080
Knowing I liked to play
with knives and sticks,

259
00:23:23,640 --> 00:23:24,920
he found a master to teach me.

260
00:23:26,039 --> 00:23:27,359
When I grew up,

261
00:23:28,960 --> 00:23:31,359
I begged him to let me
perform rituals in the hall

262
00:23:32,599 --> 00:23:33,839
and to recognize him as the boss.

263
00:23:36,000 --> 00:23:37,240
In the first few years,

264
00:23:38,480 --> 00:23:40,000
he wouldn't let me go out on missions,

265
00:23:41,359 --> 00:23:42,559
saying I was too young.

266
00:23:43,200 --> 00:23:44,680
Just stay by his side, that's enough.

267
00:23:46,640 --> 00:23:47,759
When I was eighteen,

268
00:23:49,000 --> 00:23:50,000
he was ambushed.

269
00:23:52,680 --> 00:23:53,920
He only had a few men with him.

270
00:23:54,759 --> 00:23:56,480
They were blocked in an alley.

271
00:23:59,519 --> 00:24:00,839
I went crazy,

272
00:24:01,519 --> 00:24:02,640
grabbing two knives,

273
00:24:02,680 --> 00:24:03,839
and rushed in to save him.

274
00:24:33,079 --> 00:24:34,319
When I rescued him,

275
00:24:36,319 --> 00:24:37,319
he slapped me.

276
00:24:38,880 --> 00:24:39,880
He said

277
00:24:41,799 --> 00:24:42,799
even if he died,

278
00:24:45,400 --> 00:24:47,359
he wouldn't want me to
risk my life to save him.

279
00:24:50,759 --> 00:24:51,880
Afterwards,

280
00:24:53,319 --> 00:24:54,960
he told the elders,

281
00:24:55,640 --> 00:24:57,799
that I should be promoted to Red Pole.

282
00:25:01,920 --> 00:25:02,960
Big brother, sometimes,

283
00:25:07,279 --> 00:25:09,039
he's just full of contradictions.

284
00:25:15,960 --> 00:25:17,079
My sister was getting

285
00:25:20,359 --> 00:25:21,359
more and more beautiful.

286
00:25:24,160 --> 00:25:25,840
Many big shots took a liking to her.

287
00:25:27,079 --> 00:25:28,519
Qinglong tried to matchmake for her.

288
00:25:29,200 --> 00:25:30,400
She didn't want any of them.

289
00:25:32,720 --> 00:25:33,720
One day,

290
00:25:34,680 --> 00:25:36,039
she secretly told me,

291
00:25:37,480 --> 00:25:39,000
that the one she likes is big brother.

292
00:25:42,160 --> 00:25:43,599
She wants to be Qinglong's woman.

293
00:25:48,319 --> 00:25:49,599
And shortly after,

294
00:25:51,680 --> 00:25:52,960
it was my twentieth birthday.

295
00:25:56,102 --> 00:25:57,599
Big brother asked me what I wanted.

296
00:26:00,000 --> 00:26:01,000
I...

297
00:26:04,480 --> 00:26:05,480
I said...

298
00:26:06,920 --> 00:26:07,920
I want

299
00:26:08,519 --> 00:26:10,480
my sister to be your wife.

300
00:26:30,680 --> 00:26:31,680
Liuyi.

301
00:26:32,920 --> 00:26:33,920
Liuyi.

302
00:26:35,920 --> 00:26:36,920
Liuyi.

303
00:26:38,480 --> 00:26:39,559
Brother, you're here.

304
00:26:40,000 --> 00:26:41,000
What are you thinking?

305
00:26:41,960 --> 00:26:42,960
Nothing.

306
00:26:44,160 --> 00:26:45,280
You're about to turn twenty.

307
00:26:45,720 --> 00:26:46,960
What birthday gift do you want?

308
00:26:49,279 --> 00:26:50,279
Birthday?

309
00:26:53,200 --> 00:26:54,200
Whatever I want...

310
00:26:54,839 --> 00:26:55,999
will big brother agree to it?

311
00:26:56,279 --> 00:26:58,319
Of course! I care so much about you.

312
00:27:09,759 --> 00:27:10,759
I want

313
00:27:13,480 --> 00:27:14,520
my sister to be your wife.

314
00:27:15,480 --> 00:27:16,480
I hope the three of us

315
00:27:16,481 --> 00:27:17,521
can be like a real family,

316
00:27:17,839 --> 00:27:18,839
always together.

317
00:27:32,920 --> 00:27:33,920
Okay.

318
00:27:35,039 --> 00:27:36,039
I promise you.

319
00:27:38,359 --> 00:27:40,200
Brother, I knew you were the best to me.

320
00:27:47,640 --> 00:27:48,880
Big brother agreed.

321
00:27:51,359 --> 00:27:52,480
He married my sister.

322
00:27:56,640 --> 00:27:59,160
He even made me a new
pair of Qinglong dual blades.

323
00:28:00,599 --> 00:28:02,960
He also took me to meet
the elders of the gang,

324
00:28:03,480 --> 00:28:04,480
and told them

325
00:28:05,920 --> 00:28:07,720
that from now on, part
of the gang's business

326
00:28:10,480 --> 00:28:12,519
would gradually be handed to me to manage.

327
00:28:16,960 --> 00:28:17,960
From then on,

328
00:28:20,720 --> 00:28:21,840
I became his right-hand man.

329
00:28:24,680 --> 00:28:25,839
He was my boss.

330
00:28:39,640 --> 00:28:41,200
And my sister became the sister-in-law.

331
00:28:42,680 --> 00:28:44,280
I thought it would be like this forever.

332
00:28:51,960 --> 00:28:52,960
That day,

333
00:28:56,200 --> 00:28:57,559
I went to pick up my sister.

334
00:29:05,480 --> 00:29:06,720
She jumped off the building.

335
00:29:10,480 --> 00:29:11,839
And big brother was killed too...

336
00:29:20,559 --> 00:29:21,559
by

337
00:29:23,480 --> 00:29:24,720
The Qinglong dual blades

338
00:29:26,599 --> 00:29:27,640
he gave me.

339
00:29:29,519 --> 00:29:30,920
I failed to protect them.

340
00:29:32,759 --> 00:29:33,839
I failed.

341
00:29:37,359 --> 00:29:38,400
I failed.

342
00:29:40,160 --> 00:29:41,640
I failed.

343
00:29:52,039 --> 00:29:53,039
It was

344
00:29:56,039 --> 00:29:58,319
that bastard Xu Ying.

345
00:30:00,880 --> 00:30:02,359
He swapped my sister's medicine,

346
00:30:04,599 --> 00:30:06,160
causing her to relapse.

347
00:30:08,680 --> 00:30:10,279
He killed my brother

348
00:30:12,480 --> 00:30:13,559
and tried to frame me.

349
00:30:15,359 --> 00:30:16,359
The people chasing me

350
00:30:20,319 --> 00:30:21,720
were his men.

351
00:30:23,400 --> 00:30:24,400
So now,

352
00:30:26,559 --> 00:30:27,559
what are you planning to do?

353
00:30:32,400 --> 00:30:33,400
Kill him.

354
00:30:36,799 --> 00:30:37,799
Avenge my brother

355
00:30:39,880 --> 00:30:40,880
and my sister.

356
00:30:42,319 --> 00:30:43,319
Take revenge.

357
00:30:47,720 --> 00:30:48,720
Then what?

358
00:30:51,039 --> 00:30:52,039
Then...

359
00:30:53,119 --> 00:30:55,480
You joined the
Xiaoqi Hall for Qinglong.

360
00:30:56,599 --> 00:30:58,239
You'll go kill Xu Ying to take revenge.

361
00:31:00,640 --> 00:31:01,640
And after that?

362
00:31:08,240 --> 00:31:09,240
Take care of

363
00:31:10,359 --> 00:31:12,200
the brothers Qinglong left behind.

364
00:31:15,680 --> 00:31:16,759
And grow Xiaoqi Hall

365
00:31:19,400 --> 00:31:20,480
into

366
00:31:20,680 --> 00:31:21,720
the biggest gang

367
00:31:22,839 --> 00:31:24,119
in the city.

368
00:32:33,459 --> 00:32:36,338
[Work hard, make money,
buy dad a big place]

369
00:32:38,920 --> 00:32:40,160
Innocent student.

370
00:32:41,359 --> 00:32:42,359
Dad,

371
00:32:42,559 --> 00:32:43,575
I'm delivering the medicine.

372
00:32:43,599 --> 00:32:44,599
Okay.

373
00:33:16,839 --> 00:33:17,839
You walk so quietly.

374
00:33:18,200 --> 00:33:19,200
You scared me to death.

375
00:33:20,000 --> 00:33:21,000
Brother Liuyi.

376
00:33:21,839 --> 00:33:22,839
Your eyelids

377
00:33:24,039 --> 00:33:25,039
seem a little swollen.

378
00:33:27,759 --> 00:33:28,839
Rub them with an egg.

379
00:33:38,799 --> 00:33:39,799
Last night,

380
00:33:40,240 --> 00:33:41,240
don't get me wrong.

381
00:33:41,680 --> 00:33:43,040
I'm not trying to complain to you.

382
00:33:44,599 --> 00:33:45,599
I know.

383
00:33:50,359 --> 00:33:51,999
I'm not looking for your sympathy either.

384
00:33:53,519 --> 00:33:54,519
Okay.

385
00:33:56,599 --> 00:33:57,599
I...

386
00:33:59,000 --> 00:34:00,960
I just wanted to talk.

387
00:34:01,599 --> 00:34:03,039
There isn't even

388
00:34:03,160 --> 00:34:04,160
a single chicken here.

389
00:34:17,880 --> 00:34:19,280
I want beef offal for breakfast.

390
00:34:21,140 --> 00:34:21,800
Dad said

391
00:34:22,000 --> 00:34:23,720
you should take this medicine before meals.

392
00:34:23,840 --> 00:34:24,840
Here.

393
00:34:25,320 --> 00:34:25,719
I won't take it.

394
00:34:26,199 --> 00:34:27,199
It smells awful.

395
00:34:27,480 --> 00:34:27,920
Beef offal.

396
00:34:28,199 --> 00:34:29,199
No.

397
00:34:29,360 --> 00:34:30,976
Dad said the herbal medicine
must be taken before meals.

398
00:34:31,000 --> 00:34:31,800
Three times a day.
Not a single dose can be skipped.

399
00:34:32,760 --> 00:34:33,760
Three times.

400
00:34:34,199 --> 00:34:35,599
That's enough to kill a rat, right?

401
00:34:35,920 --> 00:34:36,639
Go away.

402
00:34:36,880 --> 00:34:37,880
It's spilled.

403
00:34:39,400 --> 00:34:40,400
Dad,

404
00:34:40,519 --> 00:34:42,559
someone's trying to feed
your medicine to the rats.

405
00:34:44,760 --> 00:34:46,160
Who dares to mess with my medicine?

406
00:34:46,280 --> 00:34:47,280
Him.

407
00:34:47,400 --> 00:34:48,495
Gangsters have no education.

408
00:34:48,519 --> 00:34:49,575
Don't you have any education either?

409
00:34:49,599 --> 00:34:50,360
If the patient refuses the medicine,

410
00:34:50,400 --> 00:34:51,480
there's nothing you can do?

411
00:34:51,639 --> 00:34:52,800
And you've studied so much.

412
00:34:53,760 --> 00:34:54,760
When people get sick,

413
00:34:54,800 --> 00:34:56,440
how can they get better without medicine?

414
00:34:58,039 --> 00:34:59,400
Bitter medicine is good for you.

415
00:35:00,519 --> 00:35:01,519
Chusan.

416
00:35:06,880 --> 00:35:07,920
Chusan, don't laugh.

417
00:35:07,960 --> 00:35:08,960
Hold his hands down.

418
00:35:09,000 --> 00:35:10,000
Don't move.

419
00:35:16,480 --> 00:35:16,800
Dad,

420
00:35:17,039 --> 00:35:18,119
you really know what to do.

421
00:35:18,760 --> 00:35:20,480
How could a doctor not handle a patient?

422
00:35:20,920 --> 00:35:21,239
Chusan,

423
00:35:21,800 --> 00:35:23,080
remember to change his dressing.

424
00:35:27,719 --> 00:35:28,719
You little punk.

425
00:35:29,239 --> 00:35:30,480
Don't let me get better.

426
00:35:31,800 --> 00:35:32,800
If I do get better,

427
00:35:33,840 --> 00:35:35,480
I'll be the first to kill you.

428
00:35:55,239 --> 00:35:56,239
It might hurt a little.

429
00:36:08,480 --> 00:36:09,480
It'll be over soon.

430
00:37:01,159 --> 00:37:02,159
Brother Liuyi.

431
00:37:02,280 --> 00:37:03,840
You need to sit up a bit.

432
00:38:11,880 --> 00:38:12,920
Put more strength into it.

433
00:38:14,239 --> 00:38:15,239
What?

434
00:38:16,639 --> 00:38:17,999
I said, put more strength into it.

435
00:38:31,639 --> 00:38:32,639
What are you doing?

436
00:38:34,000 --> 00:38:34,679
Wiping your butt.

437
00:38:35,000 --> 00:38:36,000
Stick your butt out.

438
00:39:07,559 --> 00:39:08,839
Why are you using so much force?

439
00:39:10,559 --> 00:39:12,199
Do you want me to wipe the front for you?

440
00:39:13,840 --> 00:39:14,880
I can do the front myself.

441
00:39:35,840 --> 00:39:36,840
Do you want me to help?

442
00:39:39,519 --> 00:39:40,519
I can do it myself.

443
00:40:13,000 --> 00:40:13,719
Chusan.

444
00:40:14,000 --> 00:40:15,000
Time to get up.

445
00:40:15,400 --> 00:40:16,400
I'm coming in.

446
00:40:17,360 --> 00:40:17,920
Chusan.

447
00:40:18,119 --> 00:40:19,800
I made bone soup for you and your friend.

448
00:40:20,000 --> 00:40:21,000
Come down and drink it.

449
00:40:23,719 --> 00:40:24,840
Slow down, slow down.

450
00:40:30,760 --> 00:40:32,239
Is this your friend?

451
00:40:32,480 --> 00:40:33,239
Very handsome.

452
00:40:33,400 --> 00:40:34,400
Hello.

453
00:40:34,880 --> 00:40:36,159
Wash up and come down to eat.

454
00:40:37,199 --> 00:40:38,199
The food will get cold.

455
00:40:41,519 --> 00:40:42,519
Why did you kick me?

456
00:40:43,239 --> 00:40:44,239
Who kicked you?

457
00:40:52,800 --> 00:40:54,120
Sister Fei, this is so delicious.

458
00:40:55,039 --> 00:40:56,558
I'm going to eat everything

459
00:40:56,559 --> 00:40:57,559
for breakfast.

460
00:40:58,239 --> 00:40:59,239
Sister Fei,

461
00:40:59,679 --> 00:41:00,559
what you cooked is even

462
00:41:00,679 --> 00:41:03,159
better than what the most
expensive chefs in Harbor City make.

463
00:41:03,199 --> 00:41:03,920
Chusan,

464
00:41:04,079 --> 00:41:06,000
your friend really knows how to talk.

465
00:41:07,599 --> 00:41:09,480
Brother, come help a bit.

466
00:41:10,000 --> 00:41:11,000
Okay, okay.

467
00:41:11,079 --> 00:41:12,280
I'll help, I'll help.

468
00:41:13,960 --> 00:41:15,720
I didn't expect you'd
be so good at talking.

469
00:41:27,199 --> 00:41:28,199
Eat this.

470
00:41:28,519 --> 00:41:29,719
No way.

471
00:41:58,239 --> 00:41:59,239
Open the door!

472
00:42:00,280 --> 00:42:01,280
Open up!

473
00:42:02,119 --> 00:42:02,639
Hurry up.

474
00:42:02,880 --> 00:42:04,159
Who is it?

475
00:42:05,000 --> 00:42:06,800
Why are you making noise so early?

476
00:42:10,000 --> 00:42:11,000
Where?

477
00:42:11,760 --> 00:42:12,880
Sir!

478
00:42:13,239 --> 00:42:14,360
Who are you looking for?

479
00:42:15,480 --> 00:42:16,480
Sir!

480
00:42:17,920 --> 00:42:18,199
Where is he?

481
00:42:18,760 --> 00:42:19,760
He's not here.

482
00:42:21,039 --> 00:42:22,039
Sir, only my son lives upstairs.

483
00:42:22,040 --> 00:42:23,400
Don't get in the way.

484
00:42:25,599 --> 00:42:26,000
Sir.
Sir.

485
00:42:26,960 --> 00:42:27,559
Nobody else is upstairs.

486
00:42:27,560 --> 00:42:28,920
Just my son alone.

487
00:42:34,159 --> 00:42:35,400
Sirs, sirs!

488
00:42:39,360 --> 00:42:41,239
Sirs, let's talk this out.

489
00:42:41,480 --> 00:42:43,079
My son has gone to school.

490
00:43:24,599 --> 00:43:25,599
Old man.

491
00:43:26,159 --> 00:43:28,639
Your son is that university
student from the city fort, right?

492
00:43:29,079 --> 00:43:30,079
Yes, yes, yes.

493
00:43:30,719 --> 00:43:32,095
He's loved reading since he was a child.

494
00:43:32,119 --> 00:43:33,360
Besides going to college,

495
00:43:33,639 --> 00:43:34,879
he hasn't really achieved much.

496
00:43:36,159 --> 00:43:38,159
Sirs, let me treat you.

497
00:43:38,239 --> 00:43:39,239
There's noise downstairs.

498
00:43:49,920 --> 00:43:50,920
What are you doing?

499
00:43:54,639 --> 00:43:55,639
Nothing.

500
00:43:56,159 --> 00:43:56,840
Then why are you moving around?

501
00:43:57,159 --> 00:43:58,159
My back hurts.

502
00:44:02,639 --> 00:44:03,639
Sirs,

503
00:44:03,719 --> 00:44:04,960
I told you, no one's here.

504
00:44:09,559 --> 00:44:10,559
Go back.

505
00:44:28,880 --> 00:44:29,880
Let's go.

506
00:44:34,119 --> 00:44:35,119
They must be around here.

507
00:44:35,199 --> 00:44:36,199
Search house by house.

508
00:44:40,679 --> 00:44:41,119
Are you okay?

509
00:44:41,159 --> 00:44:42,159
Don't make a sound.

510
00:44:42,599 --> 00:44:43,599
Quiet.

511
00:44:46,199 --> 00:44:47,199
Move.

512
00:44:47,840 --> 00:44:48,840
Go.

513
00:44:59,320 --> 00:45:00,199
Are you kidding me?

514
00:45:00,239 --> 00:45:01,840
Running away with that crappy backpack?

515
00:45:01,880 --> 00:45:02,679
I have my final exam today.

516
00:45:02,760 --> 00:45:04,160
I'm afraid I won't make it in time.

517
00:45:06,920 --> 00:45:07,920
Your wound has reopened.

518
00:45:12,400 --> 00:45:13,800
Xia Liuyi, I…

519
00:45:15,239 --> 00:45:16,480
Don't call me Xia Liuyi.

520
00:45:17,159 --> 00:45:18,159
Call me Brother Liuyi.

521
00:45:19,079 --> 00:45:20,159
I'm not your underling.

522
00:45:22,599 --> 00:45:23,839
So many people begged to be my underling,

523
00:45:23,840 --> 00:45:24,840
and they couldn't.

524
00:45:25,280 --> 00:45:26,575
Plus, I'm three years older than you.

525
00:45:26,599 --> 00:45:27,799
How can I not be your brother?

526
00:45:34,519 --> 00:45:35,519
Did you grow taller?

527
00:45:37,639 --> 00:45:39,239
I've always been taller than you.

528
00:45:39,840 --> 00:45:41,199
Just not as strong as you.

529
00:45:43,159 --> 00:45:44,159
Take off your clothes.

530
00:45:47,480 --> 00:45:48,519
Take whose?

531
00:45:48,639 --> 00:45:49,639
Ours.

532
00:45:50,039 --> 00:45:50,280
I…

533
00:45:50,559 --> 00:45:51,719
Help me stop the bleeding.

534
00:45:54,559 --> 00:45:55,559
Also,

535
00:45:56,159 --> 00:45:57,159
help me with something.

536
00:45:58,800 --> 00:45:59,800
I can help you.

537
00:46:00,960 --> 00:46:02,040
But I'm not your underling.

538
00:46:02,320 --> 00:46:03,320
Shut up.

539
00:46:31,599 --> 00:46:32,840
Xia Liuyi's knife?

540
00:46:33,199 --> 00:46:34,199
Why is it here?

541
00:46:35,039 --> 00:46:35,599
I don't know.

542
00:46:35,880 --> 00:46:36,880
I know nothing.

543
00:46:37,679 --> 00:46:38,679
I don't know.

544
00:46:39,159 --> 00:46:40,480
Tell me, where is Xia Liuyi?

545
00:46:40,760 --> 00:46:41,880
I-I don't know.

546
00:46:42,119 --> 00:46:43,119
I'll stab you.

547
00:46:48,000 --> 00:46:49,920
He forced me to throw this knife.

548
00:46:51,239 --> 00:46:53,480
He said to wait for me
at the Xiaoqi Studio.

549
00:46:54,360 --> 00:46:56,079
You better not play tricks.

550
00:46:56,880 --> 00:46:57,880
Go tell Brother Xu.

551
00:46:58,079 --> 00:46:59,256
Tell him Xia Liuyi has been found.

552
00:46:59,280 --> 00:47:00,199
At Xiaoqi Studio.

553
00:47:00,239 --> 00:47:01,519
Then what about this kid?

554
00:47:01,800 --> 00:47:03,280
I've told you everything.

555
00:47:05,119 --> 00:47:07,760
Can you... let me go?

556
00:47:07,960 --> 00:47:09,159
What?

557
00:47:09,519 --> 00:47:10,519
Take him with you.

558
00:47:10,800 --> 00:47:13,015
If we fail, at least we have
him to report to Brother Xu.

559
00:47:13,039 --> 00:47:13,320
Go.
Go.

560
00:47:14,360 --> 00:47:15,360
Move.

561
00:47:16,519 --> 00:47:17,519
Go.

562
00:47:18,599 --> 00:47:19,599
Let's go.

563
00:48:24,159 --> 00:48:26,559
Qinglong really hid the ledgers with you.

564
00:48:30,632 --> 00:48:32,913
You had a student help you
get rid of the bloody clothes,

565
00:48:33,159 --> 00:48:34,959
making me think you
left the city stronghold.

566
00:48:35,480 --> 00:48:36,480
Xia Liuyi,

567
00:48:36,580 --> 00:48:37,960
how could you be so stupid?
